---
// src/components/FAQ.astro
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-200" id="faq">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-blue-600 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4">
                Common Questions
            </h2>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
                No Sales Fluff.
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Everything you need to know about money, timelines, and ownership.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            
            <details name="faq-group" class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden open:bg-white open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg">
                    <span>Why shouldn't I just run Google Ads?</span>
                    <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">
                    Google Ads is like <strong>renting a house</strong>. You pay expensive rent every month, and the second you stop paying, you get kicked out (traffic stops). 
                    <br><br>
                    What we build is like <strong>buying a house</strong>. You pay once to build the asset, and it generates customers for years for free.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details name="faq-group" class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden open:bg-white open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg">
                    <span>I already have a website. Can you just fix that one?</span>
                    <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">
                    <strong>No. We don't patch old sites. We replace them.</strong>
                    <br><br>
                    Why? <strong>Speed.</strong> Old websites (built on WordPress or Wix) are usually too slow to rank well on Google. Trying to fix them is like trying to put a Ferrari engine inside a bicycle.
                    <br><br>
                    We rebuild your site on our <strong>High-Performance Architecture</strong> so it loads instantly. You keep your domain name, but you get a massive upgrade in horsepower.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details name="faq-group" class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden open:bg-white open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg">
                    <span>Are there really no monthly fees?</span>
                    <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">
                    There are <strong>zero management fees</strong> during the build.
                    <br><br>
                    After the first 3 months (after the website launch), we offer a flat <strong>RM 500/year</strong> package. This covers hosting, security, and <strong>unlimited content updates</strong>. Need to change a price, photo, or paragraph? Just text us. We do it for free.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details name="faq-group" class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden open:bg-white open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg">
                    <span>Do I own the domain and code?</span>
                    <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">
                    <strong>100%.</strong> In fact, we insist that YOU purchase the domain name on your own account.
                    <br><br>
                    This ensures no agency can ever hold your business hostage. You hold the keys to the asset.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details name="faq-group" class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden open:bg-white open:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg">
                    <span>When does the phone start ringing?</span>
                    <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">
                    We don't make fake promises. SEO is organic, so <strong>every business grows differently</strong> based on competition and market demand.
                    <br><br>
                    We build the engine for maximum speed and visibility, but organic traffic is a long-term compounder, not an overnight switch. If you need guaranteed leads *tomorrow*, ads are a safer bet.
                </div>
            </details>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>